00:12.134 --> 00:13.604
Supreme Vampiric Council.

00:13.638 --> 00:17.077
Will you do me the honor
of accompanying me on my journey

00:17.111 --> 00:18.748
around the world?

00:18.781 --> 00:21.587
-Make sure
you look after my wife.
-What? Aah! No!

00:21.620 --> 00:24.425
