is even more terrifying

00:26.830 --> 00:29.235
and mysterious than our own.

00:29.268 --> 00:30.470
Shit.

00:33.476 --> 00:35.548
-(lightning crashes)
-(thunder rumbling)

00:55.655 --> 00:57.626
-(cawing)
-(cameraman gasps)

